    "Html": "Using a DataGridTemplateColumn should work.  Here's an example where ColorItem and ColorItems are just arbitrary objects:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">\r\n<p>&lt;d</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">g</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridTemplateColumn</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Header</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;ColorItem&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">dg</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridTemplateColumn.CellTemplate</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">        &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataTemplate</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">            &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">TextBlock</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Text</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Path</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=ColorItem,</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Mode</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=OneWay}&quot; /&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">        &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataTemplate</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">    &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">dg</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridTemplateColumn.CellTemplate</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">dg</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridTemplateColumn.CellEditingTemplate</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">        &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataTemplate</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">            &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">ComboBox</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> SelectedItem</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Path</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=ColorItem,</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Mode</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=TwoWay,</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> UpdateSourceTrigger</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=PropertyChanged}&quot; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">ItemsSource</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Path</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=ColorItems}&quot;/&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">        &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataTemplate</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">    &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">dg</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridTemplateColumn.CellEditingTemplate</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">dg</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridTemplateColumn</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;</span></p>\r\n",
